ä»–ã«ã‚‚ã‚¹ãƒ”ãƒ³2ã®ä¾‹ã¨ã—ã¦ã¯é‡åŠ›æ³¢ãŒæŒ™ã’ã‚‰ã‚Œã¾ã™ã€‚ã“ã‚Œã¯ãƒ™ã‚¯ãƒˆãƒ«ã§ã¯ãªããƒ†ãƒ³ã‚½ãƒ«ã§ã™ã€‚ã‚¹ãƒ”ãƒ³0ã¯ä¾‹å¤–ã§ã€ä»»æ„ã®ç„¡é™å°å›è»¢ã«å¯¾ã—ã¦ä¸å¤‰ãªã‚‚ã®ã€ã™ãªã‚ã¡ä¸€å›è»¢ã•ã›ã‚‹ã¨ç„¡é™å›å…ƒã«æˆ»ã‚‹ã‚‚ã®ã‚’æ„å‘³ã—ã¾ã™ã€‚ã“ã®ã‚ˆã†ãªæ³¢å‹•ã‚’ã‚¹ã‚«ãƒ©ãƒ¼ã¨å‘¼ã³ã¾ã™ã€‚éŸ³æ³¢ãªã©ã®ç¸¦æ³¢ãŒãã®ä¾‹ã§ã™ã€‚</p>

<p><img src="/assets/images/astroelec/polarization_00.png" alt="ã‚¹ãƒ”ãƒ³0, 1, 2ã®æ³¢å‹•ã®ä¾‹" /></p>

<p>ä»¥ä¸‹ã¯é›»ç£æ³¢ã®ãƒ™ã‚¯ãƒˆãƒ«æ€§ã‚’åæ˜ ã—ãŸç‰©ç†é‡ã§ã‚ã‚‹ã€åå…‰çŠ¶æ…‹ã«ã¤ã„ã¦ãƒ¡ãƒ¢ã—ãŸã‚‚ã®ã§ã™ã€‚</p>

<h2 id="å˜è‰²é›»ç£æ³¢ã®åå…‰çŠ¶æ…‹">å˜è‰²é›»ç£æ³¢ã®åå…‰çŠ¶æ…‹</h2>

<p>è§’æŒ¯å‹•æ•°\(\omega\)ã®åå…‰çŠ¶æ…‹ã«ã¤ã„ã¦èª¿ã¹ã¦ã¿ã¾ã—ã‚‡ã†ã€‚ã“ã“ã§é›»ç£æ³¢ã®é€²è¡Œæ–¹å‘ã‚’\(z\)è»¸ã«å–ã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚ãã®ä½ç›¸ã‚’\(\tau=\omega t - kz\)ã¨è¡¨ã™ã¨ã€ä»»æ„ã®é›»ç£æ³¢ã®é›»å ´æˆåˆ†ã¯ä»¥ä¸‹ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«æ›¸ã‘ã¾ã™ã€‚</p>

\[\left\{ \begin{array}{c}
E_x 
= a_1 \cos (\tau + \delta_1) \\
E_y 
= a_2 \cos (\tau + \delta_2)
\end{array}
\right.\]

<p>\(\cos (\tau + \delta_1) = \cos \tau \cos \delta_1 - \sin \tau \sin \delta_1\)ãªã©ã‚ˆã‚Šã€ä¸Šå¼ã®2ã¤ã®é›»å ´ã‚’</p>

\[\left( \begin{array}{c}
\frac{E_x}{a_1} \\
\frac{E_y}{a_2}
\end{array} \right)
= \left( \begin{array}{cc}
\cos \delta_1 &amp; - \sin \delta_1 \\
\cos \delta_2 &amp; - \sin \delta_2
\end{array} \right)
\left( \begin{array}{c}
\cos \tau \\
\sin \tau
\end{array} \right) \tag{1}\]

<p>ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«è¡Œåˆ—ã‚’ç”¨ã„ãŸ1ã¤ã®å¼ã«ã¾ã¨ã‚ã¦æ›¸ãã“ã¨ãŒã§ãã¾ã™ã€‚ã“ã®ã¨ãã€(1)å¼ã«ç¾ã‚ŒãŸè¡Œåˆ—ã‚’\(A\)ã¨ã™ã‚‹ã¨ã€ãã®é€†è¡Œåˆ—ã¯</p>

\[A^{-1}
=\frac{1}{-\cos\delta_1\sin\delta_2 + \cos \delta_2 \sin\delta_1} 
\left( \begin{array}{cc}
-\sin \delta_2 &amp; \sin \delta_1 \\
-\cos \delta_2 &amp; \cos \delta_1
\end{array} \right) 
=\frac{1}{\sin \delta} 
\left( \begin{array}{cc}
-\sin \delta_2 &amp; \sin \delta_1 \\
-\cos \delta_2 &amp; \cos \delta_1
\end{array} \right) \tag{2}\]

<p>ã§ã™ã€‚ã“ã“ã§\(\delta \equiv \delta_2-\delta_1\)ã¨ã—ã¾ã—ãŸã€‚ã•ã‚‰ã«ã“ã®è»¢ç½®è¡Œåˆ—ã‚’æ±‚ã‚ã¾ã—ã‚‡ã†ã€‚</p>

\[(A^{-1})^\top
= \frac{1}{\sin \delta} 
\left( \begin{array}{cc}
-\sin \delta_2 &amp; -\cos \delta_2 \\
\sin \delta_1 &amp; \cos \delta_1
\end{array} \right) \tag{3}\]

<p>(1)å¼ã«æˆ»ã‚Šã€\(X \equiv E_x / a_1, Y \equiv E_y / a_2\)ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«ã™ã‚‹ã¨</p>

\[\left( \begin{array}{c}
X \\
Y
\end{array}\right) 
= A \left( \begin{array}{c}
\cos \tau \\
\sin \tau
\end{array}\right) \ \underbrace{\Longrightarrow}_{A^{-1} \times} \
A^{-1} \left( \begin{array}{c}
X \\
Y
\end{array}\right) 
= \left( \begin{array}{c}
\cos \tau \\
\sin \tau
\end{array}\right)\]

<p>ã“ã‚Œã®å…¨ä½“ã‚’è»¢ç½®ã•ã›ãŸã‚‚ã®ã¯</p>

\[(X, Y) (A^{-1})^\top = (\cos \tau, \sin \tau)\]

<p>ã‚ˆã‚Šã€2ã¤ã®å†…ç©ã‚’å–ã‚‹ã¨</p>

\[(X, Y) (A^{-1})^\top  A \left( \begin{array}{c}
X \\
Y
\end{array}\right) 
= (\cos \tau, \sin \tau) \left( \begin{array}{c}
\cos \tau \\
\sin \tau
\end{array}\right) 
= \cos^2 \tau + \sin^2 \tau 
= 1 \tag{4}\]

<p>ã“ã®æœ€å·¦è¾ºã«ç¾ã‚ŒãŸè¡Œåˆ—éƒ¨åˆ†ã‚’è¨ˆç®—ã—ã¾ã—ã‚‡ã†ã€‚(2), (3)å¼ã‚ˆã‚Š</p>

\[\begin{align}
(A^{-1})^T A^{-1} 
&amp;= \frac{1}{\sin^2 \delta} 
\left( \begin{array}{cc}
-\sin \delta_2 &amp; -\cos \delta_2 \\
\sin \delta_1 &amp; \cos \delta_1
\end{array} \right)
\left( \begin{array}{cc}
-\sin \delta_2 &amp; \sin \delta_1 \\
-\cos \delta_2 &amp; \cos \delta_1
\end{array} \right) 
= \frac{1}{\sin^2 \delta} 
\left( \begin{array}{cc}
1 &amp; -\cos \delta \\
-\cos \delta &amp; 1
\end{array} \right) \notag \\
&amp;\equiv \frac{1}{\sin^2 \delta} B \tag{5}
\end{align}\]

<p>ã¨ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚æœ€å¾Œã®è¡Œåˆ—éƒ¨åˆ†ã‚’\(B\)ã¨å®šç¾©ã—ã¾ã—ãŸã€‚ã§ã¯ã€ã•ã‚‰ã«ã“ã®è¡Œåˆ—\(B\)ã®å›ºæœ‰å€¤\(\lambda\)ãƒ»å›ºæœ‰ãƒ™ã‚¯ãƒˆãƒ«\(\mathbf{u}\)ã‚’æ±‚ã‚ã¾ã—ã‚‡ã†ã€‚</p>

\[B \mathbf{u} 
= \lambda \mathbf{u} \ \Longrightarrow \ 
(B-\lambda I) \mathbf{u} 
= \mathbf{0}\]

<p>\(I\)ã¯2x2ã®å˜ä½è¡Œåˆ—ã§ã™ã€‚é€†è¡Œåˆ—\((B- \lambda I)^{-1}\)ãŒå­˜åœ¨ã™ã‚‹ã¨ãã€\(\mathbf{u}=\mathbf{0}\)ã¨ãªã‚Šã€ã“ã‚Œã¯ä¸é©ã§ã™ã€‚ã‚ˆã£ã¦é€†è¡Œåˆ—ãŒå­˜åœ¨ã—ãªã„æ¡ä»¶ã¨ã—ã¦</p>

\[\begin{align}
&amp;\mathrm{det} (B-\lambda I) 
= \left| \begin{array}{cc}
1-\lambda &amp; -\cos \delta \\
-\cos \delta &amp; 1-\lambda
\end{array}\right|
=(1-\lambda)^2 -\cos^2 \delta
= \lambda^2 -2\lambda + \sin^2 \delta 
= 0 \notag \\
&amp;\Longrightarrow \ 
\lambda 
= \frac{2 \pm \sqrt{4 - 4 \sin^2 \delta}}{2} 
= 1 \pm \cos \delta \notag 
\end{align}\]

<p>\(|\cos \delta| \leq 1\)ã‚ˆã‚Šã€å›ºæœ‰å€¤\(\lambda\)ã¯\(\delta\)ã«é–¢ã‚ã‚‰ãšã€2ã¤ã¨ã‚‚æ­£ã®å€¤ã‚’ã¨ã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚<br />
è¡Œåˆ—\(B\)ã®å›ºæœ‰å€¤ã‚’ãã‚Œãã‚Œ\(\lambda_1 = 1+\cos \delta, \lambda_2 = 1-\cos \delta\)ã¨ãŠãã¾ã—ã‚‡ã†ã€‚ã¾ãŸ\(\lambda_1, \lambda_2\)ã«å¯¾å¿œã™ã‚‹å›ºæœ‰ãƒ™ã‚¯ãƒˆãƒ«ã‚’ãã‚Œãã‚Œ\(\mathbf{u}_1 =(a, b), \mathbf{u}_2=(c, d)\)ã¨ã—ã¾ã™ã€‚</p>

\[B \mathbf{u}_1 
= \left( \begin{array}{cc}
 1 &amp; - \cos \delta \\
 - \cos \delta &amp; 1
\end{array} \right) 
\left( \begin{array}{c}
a \\
b
\end{array} \right) 
= \left( \begin{array}{c}
a - b\cos \delta\\
b - a\cos \delta
\end{array} \right) 
= \lambda_1 {\bf u}_1 
= \left( \begin{array}{c}
a+a \cos \delta \\
b+ b \cos \delta
\end{array} \right) \ \Longrightarrow \ 
a
= -b\]

<p>ã‚ˆã£ã¦è¦æ ¼åŒ–ã•ã‚ŒãŸå›ºæœ‰ãƒ™ã‚¯ãƒˆãƒ«ã¯</p>

\[\mathbf{u}_1 
= \frac{1}{\sqrt{2}} \left( \begin{array}{c}
1 \\
-1
\end{array} \right)\]

\[B \mathbf{u}_2 
= \left( \begin{array}{cc}
 1 &amp; - \cos \delta \\
 - \cos \delta &amp; 1
\end{array} \right) 
\left( \begin{array}{c}
c \\
d
\end{array} \right) 
= \left( \begin{array}{c}
c - d\cos \delta\\
d- c\cos \delta
\end{array} \right) 
= \lambda_2 {\bf u}_2 
= \left( \begin{array}{c}
c- c\cos \delta \\
d- d \cos \delta
\end{array} \right) \ \Longrightarrow \ 
c= d\]

<p>ã‚ˆã£ã¦è¦æ ¼åŒ–ã•ã‚ŒãŸå›ºæœ‰ãƒ™ã‚¯ãƒˆãƒ«ã¯</p>

\[\mathbf{u}_2 
= \frac{1}{\sqrt{2}} \left( \begin{array}{c}
1 \\
1
\end{array} \right)\]

<p>æ¬¡ã«è¡Œåˆ—\(B\)ã®å¯¾è§’åŒ–ã‚’è€ƒãˆã¾ã™ã€‚å¯¾è§’åŒ–ã•ã›ã‚‹ãŸã‚ã®ãƒ¦ãƒ‹ã‚¿ãƒªè¡Œåˆ—ã‚’\(U\)ã¨ã™ã‚‹ã¨ã€2ã¤ã®å›ºæœ‰ãƒ™ã‚¯ãƒˆãƒ«ã‚ˆã‚Š</p>

\[U 
= \frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\left( \begin{array}{cc}
1 &amp; 1 \\
-1 &amp; 1
\end{array} \right) \tag{6}\]

<p>ãã—ã¦</p>

\[U^{-1} 
= \frac{1}{\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}} |1\cdot 1 - 1 \cdot (-1)|} \left( \begin{array}{cc}
1 &amp; -1\\
1 &amp; 1
\end{array} \right) 
= \frac{1}{\sqrt{2}} \left( \begin{array}{cc}
1 &amp; -1\\
1 &amp; 1
\end{array} \right) 
= U^T \tag{7}\]

<p>ä»¥ä¸Šã‹ã‚‰</p>

\[U^{-1} B U
= \left( \begin{array}{cc}
\lambda_1 &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; \lambda_2
\end{array} \right) \ \Longrightarrow \Â 
B 
= U \left( \begin{array}{cc}
\lambda_1 &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; \lambda_2
\end{array} \right) U^{-1} \tag{8}\]

<p>ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚(8)å¼ã‚’(4)å¼ã«ä»£å…¥ã™ã‚‹ã¨</p>

\[\frac{1}{\sin^2 \delta} (X, Y) U \left( \begin{array}{cc}
\lambda_1 &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; \lambda_2
\end{array} \right) U^{-1} \left( \begin{array}{c}
X \\
Y
\end{array} \right) 
= 1\]

<p>ã“ã“ã§</p>

\[\left( \begin{array}{c}
\xi \\
\eta
\end{array} \right) = U^{-1} \left( \begin{array}{c}
X \\
Y
\end{array} \right)\]

<p>ã¨ãŠãã¨</p>

\[(\xi, \eta) 
= \left( U^{-1} \left( \begin{array}{c} 
X \\ 
Y
\end{array} \right) \right)^T 
= (X, Y) (U^{-1})^T 
\underbrace{=}_{(7)} (X, Y) U\]

<p>ã‚ˆã‚Š</p>

\[(\xi, \eta) \left( \begin{array}{cc}
\lambda_1 &amp; 0\\
0 &amp; \lambda_2
\end{array} \right) \left( \begin{array}{c}
\xi \\
\eta \end{array}\right) 
= \lambda_1 \xi^2 + \lambda_2 \eta^2 
= \sin^2 \delta 
= (1-\cos \delta) (1+\cos \delta)\]

<p>ã“ã“ã‹ã‚‰\(\delta = 0, 2\pi, 4\pi, \dots\)ã®ã¨ãã¯\(\xi=0\)ã€\(\delta = \pi, 3\pi, \dots\)ã®ã¨ãã¯\(\eta=0\)ã¨ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚ã‚ˆã£ã¦</p>

\[\left\{ \begin{array}{ll}
\xi = 0 &amp; (\delta = 2n\pi) \\
\eta = 0 &amp; (\delta = (2n+1)\pi) \\
\frac{\xi^2}{1-\cos \delta} + \frac{\eta^2}{1+ \cos \delta} = 1 &amp; ({\rm otherwise})
\end{array} \right. \tag{9}\]

<p>ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚ãŸã ã—\(n=0, 1, 2, \dots\)ã§ã™ã€‚</p>

